{"introduce": ["\n\n                    <div class=\"class-detail-text\">\n                                                <h1 class=\"class-summary-title\">课程简介</h1>\n                        <!--<div class=\"class-summary\"></div>-->\n                        <div class=\"class-summary\"><p style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">照看好生命和灵魂，让它们有一个好的状态，是你的基本责任。&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">——周国平</span></strong></p><p line=\"zn7G\" linespacing=\"115\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(234, 34, 0);\">&nbsp;年轻的我们总以为这样就能过好一生&nbsp;</span></p><p line=\"bqGq\" class=\"\" linespacing=\"115\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">为了过好这一生，我们每个人似乎都在不遗余力地做着各种努力：</span></p><p line=\"6vtw\" linespacing=\"115\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">定了5个早间闹钟、逼自己每周认识一个新“朋友”、斥“巨资”办了健身房年卡、加入了各种打卡行动、收藏各种可能有用的文章……</span></p><p line=\"Z5ZF\" linespacing=\"115\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">但是，每次好不容易迈出了第一步后，就没后文了。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(234, 34, 0);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">为了缓解焦虑所做的一切尝试最后却让我们更焦虑了。</span></strong></span></p><p line=\"kkFk\" linespacing=\"115\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">渐渐地我们成了“佛系青年”，不争不抢，无欲无求。可是，夜深人静时， 空虚无助、迷茫沮丧深深袭来，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">承认自己佛系，有时只是无助的自嘲，但又能怎么办呢？内心那一丝尚存的渴望与追求，遇到残酷的现实，就让人陷入深深的无奈与绝望中。</span></strong></span></p><p line=\"iMhe\" linespacing=\"115\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">为了过好这一生，我们也总试图从社会的标准中找到答案：</span></p><p line=\"pTqG\" linespacing=\"115\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">你可能内向敏感，恐惧社交，脆弱自卑，听了很多别人的建议想要打开自己，让自己更阳光；</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">你可能外向开朗，害怕独处，积极阳光，但总是被别人说太过聒噪，不够沉稳，于是你总是克制自己，憋屈自己，学做一只乖乖女。</span></p><p line=\"kigG\" linespacing=\"115\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">我们都在尽力活成别人眼中更完美的样子，看到朋友圈任何一种可以解决问题的方式就马上打开收藏学习，殊不知，<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">方法都是别人的，生活却是自己的。</strong></span></p><p line=\"pooL\" linespacing=\"115\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">我们穷极一生都在发掘更好的自己，努力过更好的一生，探寻生命真正的意义。现实中，却在“真实的自己”、“自己想成为的样子”、“别人期待你成为的样子”中来回摇摆，疲惫地应对这三者之间持续产生的种种矛盾。</span></strong></p><p line=\"iWEu\" linespacing=\"115\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">这个世界上是否存在一种真理，能“超越”这些所谓的现实，让我们真正获得“内心的安宁”？<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">我们到底应该如何度过这一生，才不至于在年迈时后悔？</strong></span></p><p line=\"y8uS\" linespacing=\"115\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(234, 34, 0);\">&nbsp;心理学VS哲学&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(234, 34, 0);\">&nbsp;听大咖对谈，如何过好这一生？&nbsp;</span></p><p line=\"2NKm\" linespacing=\"115\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">新年伊始，我们有幸请来</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(234, 34, 0);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">著名哲学家周国平，著名心理学家申荷永</strong></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">进行对话，这将是一次心理学与哲学的巅峰对话，两位老师还将通过分享他们的人生经历，和我们来一起探索“如何过好这一生”。</strong></span></p><p line=\"nGS6\" linespacing=\"115\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">他们可能是最适合与我们一起探讨这个话题的长者了。</span></strong></p><p line=\"nGS6\" linespacing=\"115\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">有一句话说，物理的尽头是数学，数学的尽头是哲学，哲学的尽头是神学，</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">我们诉诸经济、物理、数学等找不到答案的事情，或许哲学可以；</span></p><p line=\"oUd9\" class=\"\" linespacing=\"115\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">而在尼采说“上帝已死”的人文主义时代，我们很多事情的答案，还需要回归人“心”，这也是我们心理学的作用。</span></strong></p><p line=\"G0F2\" linespacing=\"115\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" hiragino=\"\" 