ng: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 12px;\">东方心理分析研究院创办人，“心理分析与中国文化国际论坛”主要组织者，爱诺思（Eranos）基金会“东西方文化圆桌会议”主讲人（1997，2007），著有：《心理分析：理解与体验》、《中国文化心理学心要》和《洗心岛之梦》等。</span></p><p line=\"9Ic2\" linespacing=\"115\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(234, 34, 0);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">认识自己与成为自己，是我们一生中最重要的事情。</span></strong></span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">——申荷永</span></strong></p><p line=\"ulIV\" linespacing=\"115\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-